title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Apr 27 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Apr 27 2022
description:
How did Joe Biden make $11 million in one year? Clay says, "I think when Donald Trump got elected, Joe Biden thought his political career was over and he just turned to Hunter Biden and he said, 'Let's get rich.'" On Hunter Biden and the pandemic, rigged Twitter changed history. Musk accused of sexism for Twitter criticism. Psaki claims ignorance on Joe Biden's meetings with Hunter Biden's business partner. Representative Marjorie Taylor Greene joins C&B to talk about the left's attempt to take her off the ballot, a thwarting that Buck had said "attacks Democracy." Independence Day II and Clay's favorite animated movie. C&B break down Biden's student loan scheme.

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck
